Package: libpam-truenas
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         libpam0g,
         libkeyutils1,
         libjansson4,
         libuuid1,
         libtruenas-scram1,
         libtruenas-pwenc1
Description: PAM module for TrueNAS authentication
 This PAM module provides SCRAM-SHA-512 authentication, session management,
 and account security features for TrueNAS using the Linux kernel keyring.
 .
 Features include:
  * SCRAM-SHA-512 challenge-response authentication
  * API key authentication
  * Session tracking and limiting

Package: python3-truenas-pam-utils
Section: python
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         python3-truenas-pykeyring
Description: Python utilities for TrueNAS PAM session management
 This package provides Python utilities for managing PAM sessions and
 faillog entries stored in the Linux kernel keyring.
 .
 Includes:
  * Session iterator for enumerating active sessions
  * Faillog iterator for viewing authentication failures
  * Session statistics and management tools
